reviews.text: Good station for the local Nutbournanians, but for goodness sake British Rail, give them another ticket machine! You have to arrive early if you don’t have your ticket and then run back over the road, which if the barriers come down you can’t! Good bin, but they don’t like you putting dog poop in it, so dog walkers, think again!
Ticket machine worked fine for the seven days we used the station, ideal for where we were and were we wanted to go. Simple station. No parking.

Have to come here nearly everyday. Ticket machine never works correctly so I have to always ask the man working at the gates to let me through, and it's a problem when they are not there. Worst of all it seems to be only Nutbourne having this problem.
